1) There are a number of different utilities in these directories.

./system/pbang -- Needed for the installation of the LPM kernel. See the kernel readme.

./reporters/gz_provd -- Tools for storing provenance using the GZip library
./reporters/pg_provd -- Tools for storing provenance using PostGreSQL
./reporters/neo_provd -- Tools for storing provenance using Neo4j
./reporters/snap_provd -- Tools for storing provenance using the SNAP library
./reporters/spade_provd -- Tools for converting LPM provenance into SPADE provenance

There are READMES in each subdirectory with more information.

2) Dependencies

Good things to install in order for this code to work:

# yum install make gcc ncurses-devel rpmdevtools yum-utils qt3-devel libXi-devel kernel-devel libattr-devel libuuid-devel db4-devel

or 

# apt-get install subversion build-essential uuid-dev attr-dev zlib1g-dev ncurses-dev
